## FEATURE 2: Cow Vacuum Forgiveness

When the beam deactivates, give a brief "vacuum" grace period where nearby abducting cows get pulled faster toward the UFO. This prevents the frustration of cows almost reaching the UFO then floating away.

In game.js:
1. Add `beamDeactivateTimer` variable (starts at 0)
2. In updateUFO, when beam transitions from active to inactive (the existing `!beamActive && ufo.beamActive` check), set `beamDeactivateTimer = 0.3`
3. Decrement `beamDeactivateTimer` each frame
4. In updateCows, in the abducting state, add a check:
```javascript
// Vacuum forgiveness: pull cow toward UFO faster if beam just deactivated
if (beamDeactivateTimer > 0) {
  const ufoCx = ufo.x + ufo.w / 2;
  const ufoCy = ufo.y + ufo.h / 2;
  const cowCx = cow.x + cow.w / 2;
  const cowCy = cow.y + cow.h / 2;
