[subagent] You are adding polish features to "Udderly Abduction: Barrage" at "C:\Users\koalo\Desktop\Udderly Abduction Barrage".

READ game.js, audio.js, and src/balance.js FULLY before making changes.

Key context:
- BALANCE object in src/balance.js (window.BALANCE)
- Event bus: GameEvents.on(EVT.xxx, fn) in game.js
- Bullet pool: bulletPool[], spawnBullet(), each bullet has .speed, .color, .radius, .alive
