[subagent] You are wiring narrative systems into "Udderly Abduction: Barrage" at "C:\Users\koalo\Desktop\Udderly Abduction Barrage".

READ game.js, src/narrative.js, src/balance.js, and index.html FULLY first.

The game already has:
- `window.NARRATIVE` object with waveBanners, crew callouts, timeline, goldenProphecy, gameOverLines, hayseed intercepts, and utility functions (getWaveBanner, getTimeline, getHayseed, getGameOverLine, pick)
- `window.BALANCE.narrative` with enabled, calloutDuration, loreDuration, calloutCooldown
- Event bus: GameEvents.on(EVT.COW_COLLECTED, fn) etc.
- Tutorial system: tutorialActive, showTutorial(), renderTutorial()
- Wave banner system: levelBannerText, levelBannerTimer
- Boss freeze system: bossFreezeTimer, bossFreezeName
- Game over screen rendering
- drawText(text, x, y, color, scale) and drawTextCentered(text, y, color, scale)

You need to do TWO things:

## TASK 1: Wire Narrative Into Game Systems

### 1a. Add narrative.js to index.html
Add `<script src="src/narrative.js"></script>` AFTER events.js and BEFORE audio.js in index.html.

### 1b. Add crew callout display system to game.js
Add state variables:
```javascript
let crewCallout = null;  // { speaker: 'VOXXA', text: '...', timer: 0, color: '#fff' }
let crewCalloutCooldown = 0;
```

Add a function:
```javascript
function showCrewCallout(speaker, text, color) {
  if (!BALANCE.narrative.enabled || !BALANCE.narrative.crewCalloutsEnabled) return;
  if (crewCalloutCooldown > 0) return;
  crewCallout = { speaker: speaker, text: text, timer: BALANCE.narrative.calloutDuration, color: color || '#ffffff' };
  crewCalloutCooldown = BALANCE.narrative.calloutCooldown;
}
```

Decay timers in updatePlaying:
```javascript
if (crewCallout) {
  crewCallout.timer -= dt;
  if (crewCallout.timer <= 0) crewCallout = null;
}
if (crewCalloutCooldown > 0) crewCalloutCooldown -= dt;
```

Render function (call in renderPlaying, before HUD, after tutorial):
```javascript
function renderCrewCallout() {
  if (!crewCallout) return;
  const alpha = Math.min(1, crewCallout.timer / 0.3); // fade out in last 0.3s
  ctx.globalAlpha = alpha * 0.9;

  // Speaker name + text at top-right area
  const fullText = crewCallout.speaker + ': ' + crewCallout.text;
  const tw = textWidth(fullText, 1);
  const px = W - tw - 6;
  const py = 22; // below HUD bar

  // Dark background
  ctx.fillStyle = '#000000';
  ctx.fillRect(px - 3, py - 2, tw + 8, 11);

  // Speaker name in their color, text in white
  const nameW = textWidth(crewCallout.speaker + ': ', 1);
  ctx.globalAlpha = alpha;
  drawText(crewCallout.speaker + ': ', px, py, crewCallout.color, 1);
  drawText(crewCallout.text, px + nameW, py, '#ffffff', 1);
  ctx.globalAlpha = 1;
}
```

### 1c. Wire crew callouts to game events

Add event listeners (near the existing COW_COLLECTED listeners):

```javascript
// Voxxa: high combo callout
GameEvents.on(EVT.COW_COLLECTED, function(d) {
  if (d.combo >= 8 && NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.voxxa) {
    showCrewCallout('VOXXA', NARRATIVE.pick(NARRATIVE.crew.voxxa.highCombo), '#ff44ff');
  }
});

// Blinx: golden cow spawn notification
// (This needs to be called from cow spawning, not collection. Add it in updateSpawning where cows are created)
```

In updateSpawning, after a cow is pushed to the array, check if it's golden:
```javascript
if (cow.cowType === 'golden' && NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.blinx) {
  showCrewCallout('BLINX', NARRATIVE.pick(NARRATIVE.crew.blinx.goldenCowSpawn), '#44ff44');
}
```

In updateSpawning, after a bull cow is spawned:
```javascript
if (cow.cowType === 'bull' && NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.blinx && Math.random() < 0.5) {
  showCrewCallout('BLINX', NARRATIVE.pick(NARRATIVE.crew.blinx.bullSpawn), '#44ff44');
}
```

K-RENCH on power-up collection. Find where applyPowerup is called and add:
```javascript
// After applyPowerup(pu.type) call:
if (NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.krench && NARRATIVE.crew.krench.powerup[pu.type]) {
  showCrewCallout('K-RENCH', NARRATIVE.crew.krench.powerup[pu.type], '#44ddff');
}
```

K-RENCH on bomb use. In useBomb():
```javascript
if (NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.krench) {
  showCrewCallout('K-RENCH', NARRATIVE.pick(NARRATIVE.crew.krench.bombUsed), '#44ddff');
}
```

BLINX on low HP. In the bullet collision section where ufo.hp-- happens:
```javascript
if (ufo.hp <= 2 && NARRATIVE.crew && NARRATIVE.crew.blinx) {
  showCrewCallout('BLINX', NARRATIVE.pick(NARRATIVE.crew.blinx.lowHp), '#ffff44');
}
```

### 1d. Narrative wave banners

In startLevel(), modify the levelBannerText to use narrative data:
```javascript
if (BALANCE.narrative.enabled && NARRATIVE.getWaveBanner) {
  const banner = NARRATIVE.getWaveBanner(level);
  levelBannerText = banner.title;
  // Store subtitle for rendering
  levelBannerSubtitle = banner.subtitle;
} else {
  levelBannerText = 'LEVEL ' + level;
  levelBannerSubtitle = '';
}
```

Add `let levelBannerSubtitle = '';` to state variables.

In the level banner rendering section (find where levelBannerText is drawn), add the subtitle below:
```javascript
