### 1g. Menu framing

On the menu screen, change the leaderboard header. Find where 'HIGH SCORES' is drawn and wrap it:
```javascript
const lbTitle = (BALANCE.narrative.enabled && NARRATIVE.leaderboardTitle) ? NARRATIVE.leaderboardTitle : 'HIGH SCORES';
```

## TASK 2: Golden Cow Prophecy System

### 2a. Persistent lore state
```javascript
let goldenLoreIndex = 0;
let loreFragment = null; // { text, timer }

function loadLoreProgress() {
  try {
    const data = localStorage.getItem('udderlyBarrage_lore');
    if (data) goldenLoreIndex = parseInt(data) || 0;
  } catch(e) { goldenLoreIndex = 0; }
}

function saveLoreProgress() {
  try { localStorage.setItem('udderlyBarrage_lore', String(goldenLoreIndex)); } catch(e) {}
}

function showLoreFragment(text) {
  loreFragment = { text: text, timer: BALANCE.narrative.loreDuration || 3.5 };
}
```

Call loadLoreProgress() at init (near loadLeaderboard).

### 2b. Trigger on golden cow collection

Add a COW_COLLECTED listener:
```javascript
GameEvents.on(EVT.COW_COLLECTED, function(d) {
  if (!BALANCE.narrative.enabled || !BALANCE.narrative.goldenLoreEnabled) return;
  if (d.type !== 'golden') return;
  if (!NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy || goldenLoreIndex >= NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy.length) return;

  showLoreFragment(NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy[goldenLoreIndex]);
  goldenLoreIndex++;
  saveLoreProgress();
});
```

### 2c. Render lore fragment

Add to updatePlaying:
```javascript
if (loreFragment) {
  loreFragment.timer -= dt;
  if (loreFragment.timer <= 0) loreFragment = null;
}
```

Render function (call in renderPlaying, prominent center position):
```javascript
function renderLoreFragment() {
  if (!loreFragment) return;

  const alpha = Math.min(1, Math.min(loreFragment.timer / 0.5, (BALANCE.narrative.loreDuration - loreFragment.timer + 0.01) / 0.5));
  ctx.globalAlpha = alpha;

  // Golden background bar
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(40, 30, 0, 0.8)';
  const tw = textWidth(loreFragment.text, 1);
  const px = Math.floor(W / 2 - tw / 2) - 4;
  const py = 55;
  ctx.fillRect(px - 2, py - 3, tw + 12, 14);

  // Golden border
  ctx.fillStyle = '#665500';
  ctx.fillRect(px - 3, py - 4, tw + 14, 1);
  ctx.fillRect(px - 3, py + 11, tw + 14, 1);

  // Text in gold
  drawTextCentered(loreFragment.text, py, '#ffdd44', 1);

  // Prophecy progress
  const progText = 'PROPHECY ' + goldenLoreIndex + '/' + NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy.length;
  drawTextCentered(progText, py + 10, '#aa8822', 1);

  ctx.globalAlpha = 1;
}
```

### 2d. Game over prophecy progress

On the game over screen, show prophecy progress if any fragments collected. After other stats:
```javascript
if (BALANCE.narrative.enabled && goldenLoreIndex > 0 && NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy) {
  const progText = 'PROPHECY: ' + goldenLoreIndex + '/' + NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy.length;
  drawTextCentered(progText, /* appropriate y */, '#ffdd44', 1);
}
```

### 2e. Menu prophecy indicator

On the menu screen, if any lore is collected, show a small indicator:
```javascript
if (BALANCE.narrative.enabled && goldenLoreIndex > 0 && NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy) {
  const progText = 'PROPHECY: ' + goldenLoreIndex + '/' + NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy.length;
  drawTextCentered(progText, /* below leaderboard */, '#aa8822', 1);
}
```

### 2f. Completion reward

If goldenLoreIndex >= NARRATIVE.goldenProphecy.length:
- On the menu, change the leaderboard title to 'THE AWAKENED'
- Add a faint golden tint to the menu background

## IMPORTANT:
- Guard all narrative code with `if (BALANCE.narrative.enabled)` checks so it can be disabled
- Guard all NARRATIVE references with existence checks (the data file might not load)
- No narrative text should EVER pause gameplay
- Crew callouts must respect the cooldown (8s between callouts)
- Lore fragments take visual priority over crew callouts (render on top)
- Don't break any existing game behavior
- Find the EXACT render locations in game.js by reading the render functions

ACTUALLY EDIT game.js AND index.html.

