[subagent] You are wiring audio files into "Udderly Abduction: Barrage" at "C:\Users\koalo\Desktop\Udderly Abduction Barrage".

READ game.js AND audio.js fully first.

There are new MP3 files in the project directory that need to be:
1. Renamed to clean filenames
2. Wired into the game as combo announcer sounds AND level start sounds

## COMBO ANNOUNCER AUDIO FILES

These MP3 files match combo phrases in game.js (comboPhrases object at ~line 500):

| Combo | Phrase | Source File |
